---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Spirit Media — A Global Team for a Global Mission"
	description="Meet the family behind Spirit Media. We walk with Kingdom Messengers from restoration to proclamation."
>
	<main id="main-content">

		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="bg-red-600 text-white py-24 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-200 mb-4">About Us</p>
				<h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
					A Global Team for a Global Mission
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-red-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
					We walk with Kingdom Messengers from restoration to proclamation — empowering them from
					heart → message → movement.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- WHY WE EXIST -->
		<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why We Exist</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Spirit Media exists because the Good News was never meant to stop at borders. Too often,
					vision in publishing has been small, limited to markets instead of nations. But our
					Heavenly Father worthy of His story bearing fruit in all 195 nations of the earth. We
					exist to remove the barriers — the complexity, the cost, the confusion — and to equip
					Kingdom Messengers with the publishing and marketing solutions they need to multiply
					Kingdom impact and generational inheritance.
				</p>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
					What began as holy frustration became a global mandate. We are here to build sustainable
					Kingdom movements, amplify our Father's heart, and see His whisper reach every tribe,
					tongue, and nation.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- KEVIN AND SHELLY WHITE -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Kevin and Shelly White</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Kevin White is an author, speaker, and marketplace pastor with decades of experience
					planting churches, leading nonprofits, starting companies, and developing leaders
					worldwide. Together with his wife, Shelly, he co-founded and leads Spirit Media,
					Father's Heart Bible™, and Work On Yourself.
				</p>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
					As partners in both marriage and mission for nearly forty years, they are committed to
					empowering Kingdom Messengers. They live in North Carolina with their family.
				</p>

				<!-- Free Book CTA -->
				<div class="bg-red-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-200 mb-3">
						FREE BOOK from Spirit Media
					</p>
					<h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
						Father's Heart → Beloved Identity
					</h3>
					<p class="text-red-100 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						Eight billion people are asking the same question: <em>Who am I?</em> Only one voice
						holds the answer. In this powerful compact devotional, your Heavenly Father speaks
						directly to you — revealing His heart, dismantling the orphan spirit, and establishing
						your true identity as His beloved child. Come home. You belong to Him.
					</p>
					<a
						href="https://fathersheartbible.com/join"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors"
					>
						Get Your Free Book →
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- MISSION AND VISION -->
		<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-10">This is Who We Are</h2>
				<div class="space-y-8">
					<div>
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-2">Our Mission</p>
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
							We walk with Kingdom Messengers from restoration to proclamation. Empowering them
							from <strong>heart → message → movement.</strong>
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-2">Our Vision</p>
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
							For our Father's heart to be poured out on His beloved sons and daughters in all
							195 nations.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- OUR VALUES -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-3">Culture</p>
					<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
						This is the culture that carries that mission.
					</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

					<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Father's Heart</h3>
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-600 mb-3">
							Everything flows from who God is as Father.
						</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							We seek to reveal the Father Heart of God in every relationship and decision.
							We refuse orphan thinking. We build from intimacy, identity, and inheritance, not
							insecurity. We lead with love, truth, clarity, and courage. Every author, every
							partner, every team member is seen, valued, and called higher.
							<strong class="block mt-2">We build people — not just platforms.</strong>
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Faith</h3>
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-600 mb-3">
							We move where vision requires dependence on God.
						</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							We pursue bold vision, trusting our perfect and loving Heavenly Father for outcomes
							beyond our capacity. If it can be done without Him, it isn't big enough. We embrace
							bold goals, global reach, and supernatural outcomes.
							<strong class="block mt-2">We build with faith — not fear.</strong>
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Family</h3>
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-600 mb-3">
							We operate from covenants, not contracts.
						</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							We build covenant relationships and treat every author, partner, and team member
							like family. Honor and trust matters here. We celebrate together. We carry one
							another. We speak truth in love and protect unity fiercely.
							<strong class="block mt-2">Culture is not what we say — it's how we treat each other when it costs something.</strong>
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Excellence</h3>
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-600 mb-3">
							Our Father deserves our best as we seek His best.
						</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							We reject mediocrity. We refine, sharpen, improve, and elevate. From manuscript to
							marketplace, we steward every detail with intentionality.
							<strong class="block mt-2">Excellence is worship in action.</strong>
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Multiplication</h3>
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-600 mb-3">We think nations, not numbers.</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							We are not building for one launch or one market. We empower heart → message →
							movement that multiply intimacy with the Father, beloved identity, and kingdom
							inheritance across generations.
							<strong class="block mt-2">The mandate is 195 nations — and we build accordingly.</strong>
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Stewardship</h3>
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-600 mb-3">
							Nothing entrusted to us is small.
						</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							Messages carry eternity. Resources carry responsibility. Relationships carry legacy.
							We handle them with integrity, wisdom, and long-term Kingdom vision.
						</p>
					</div>

				</div>

				<div class="mt-12 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
					<p class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 leading-relaxed">
						We are not simply a publishing family.<br />
						We are part of a global movement.<br />
						<span class="text-red-600">And we will not stop until the Father's Heart bears sons and daughters in every nation.</span>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- OUR TEAM -->
		<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-3">Our Team</p>
					<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
						A Global Team for a Global Mission
					</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Our team spans the USA, India, the Philippines, and beyond — because reaching 195
						nations requires the best talent from more than one.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
					{
						[
							{ name: 'Kevin and Shelly White', role: 'CEO / Creative' },
							{ name: 'Ana Marie Barrieses', role: 'HR' },
							{ name: 'David Foster', role: 'Publishing' },
							{ name: 'Walinda Phiri', role: 'Marketing' },
							{ name: 'Justin Keishing', role: 'Events' },
							{ name: 'Jay Esteban', role: 'Production' },
							{ name: 'Michele Lewis', role: 'Production Team' },
							{ name: 'Glory Suresh', role: 'Production Team' },
							{ name: 'Suresh Bob', role: 'Production Team' },
							{ name: 'Vinit James', role: 'Production Team' },
							{ name: 'Revo Tribaco', role: 'Production Team' },
							{ name: 'Kali White', role: 'Production Team' },
						].map(({ name, role }) => (
							<div class="text-center">
								<div class="mx-auto w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
									<span class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-red-600">
										{name[0]}
									</span>
								</div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">{name}</p>
								<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-0.5">{role}</p>
							</div>
						))
					}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- WHY PARTNER -->
		<section class="bg-navy-950 text-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why Partner with Spirit Media?</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Our Father's Heart is for relationships not just results. He offers significance not
					just success. Let Spirit Media be your long-term publishing partner to prioritize our
					Father's heart → message → movement IN you while leaving His Work THROUGH you in
					His hands.
				</p>
				<blockquote class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
					<p class="font-serif text-xl italic text-white leading-relaxed">
						"Seek our Father's Kingdom above all else, and live righteously, and he will give you
						everything you need."
					</p>
					<cite class="block mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-red-400 not-italic">
						— Matthew 6:33 (FHB)
					</cite>
				</blockquote>
				<a
					href="https://spiritmedia.us/request-a-call/"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="inline-block bg-red-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors"
				>
					Partner with Us
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
